<br>
Let's review some facts, too.<br>
1) Some of these research components are used in tradeskills to make <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/secrets/LoYrecipes.htm#tailor" target="top">Cultural Caster robes</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->. Outflow by a little for that. Some I've seen aren't half bad, either, with an <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=2686&amp;source=Live" target="top">Aura of Health</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> effect on it. Judging from some of the names, might even have a focus effect, or FT1 from it (possible). That's speculation, however.<br>
<br>
2) These mobs that drop the components, confirmed so far, have been things like Enforcers and Punishers in PoJ Death Row. They are also Uncommon drops, and it seems to be random amungst <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>all</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> the possible components. Similar to pre-50 research, but somewhat more difficult to aquire.<br>
<br>
3) Exactally how many people felt compelled to max their research skill, anyways? I did as a matter of maxing my skills, but I know pleanty of others that skipped it because it was just so much easier to run without, and one burns right past the levels that you need those spells at anymore, anyways.<br>
<br>
Ya, they'll become more common. I don't believe, however, they'll drop to 5pp for the rare rare drops. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://&quot;http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52886&quot;"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.attbi.com/~c.wroten/graphics/Rhasin_sig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#333333>- </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower>The Magician's Tower</a><font color=#333333> - </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30>Magician Skills</a> <font color=#333333> - </font><a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/">The Mage Compendium</a><font color=#333333> - </font>  <br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">Upgrade your account to ezSupporter...</a></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">...and never see another ad or pop-up again</a></td></tr></table><CENTER><!-- START BOTTOM AD SCRIPT -->
